<br>
So why not let raids start reserving Hate 2nd Floor?  Just set it up like the Naggy/FG raids and make sure that if you are starting on 2nd floor you let the 1st floor raid clear everything to the ramp then start your raid. Or how about camping out in the enterance hall of the 2nd Floor the night before?  Don't know if that would work. <p>Loven Laviedemer <BR>
